The hypothesis says: for all Оҙ > 0, eventually ВҪвҖ–g nвҖ–ВІ + ВҪвҖ–g mвҖ–ВІ - вҖ–(2вҒ»В№ : в„қвүҘ0) вҖў (g n + g m)вҖ–ВІ < Оҙ. Now (2вҒ»В№ : в„қвүҘ0) вҖў (g n + g m) = (1/2) вҖў (g n + g m) = (g n + g m)/2 as a real scalar multiple. So вҖ–(2вҒ»В№ : в„қвүҘ0) вҖў (g n + g m)вҖ–ВІ = (1/4)вҖ–g n + g mвҖ–ВІ. By the parallelogram law: вҖ–g n + g mвҖ–ВІ + вҖ–g n - g mвҖ–ВІ = 2вҖ–g nвҖ–ВІ + 2вҖ–g mвҖ–ВІ. So вҖ–g n + g mвҖ–ВІ = 2вҖ–g nвҖ–ВІ + 2вҖ–g mвҖ–ВІ - вҖ–g n - g mвҖ–ВІ. Therefore ВҪвҖ–g nвҖ–ВІ + ВҪвҖ–g mвҖ–ВІ - Вј(2вҖ–g nвҖ–ВІ + 2вҖ–g mвҖ–ВІ - вҖ–g n - g mвҖ–ВІ) = ВҪвҖ–g nвҖ–ВІ + ВҪвҖ–g mвҖ–ВІ - ВҪвҖ–g nвҖ–ВІ - ВҪвҖ–g mвҖ–ВІ + ВјвҖ–g n - g mвҖ–ВІ = ВјвҖ–g n - g mвҖ–ВІ. So the hypothesis gives ВјвҖ–g n - g mвҖ–ВІ < Оҙ, i.e., вҖ–g n - g mвҖ–ВІ < 4Оҙ, hence вҖ–g n - g mвҖ– < 2вҲҡОҙ. This shows g is Cauchy. Use cauchySeq_of_le_tendsto_0 or Metric.cauchySeq_iff. Key Mathlib lemma: parallelogram_law_with_norm.
-/
private lemma komlos_cauchy [NormedAddCommGroup E] [InnerProductSpace в„қ E]
    {g : в„• вҶ’ E}
    (hg_komlos : вҲҖ Оҙ > 0, вҲғ N, вҲҖ n m, N вүӨ n вҶ’ N вүӨ m вҶ’
      2вҒ»В№ * вҖ–g nвҖ– ^ 2 + 2вҒ»В№ * вҖ–g mвҖ– ^ 2 -
        вҖ–((2 : в„қвүҘ0)вҒ»В№ : в„қвүҘ0) вҖў (g n + g m)вҖ– ^ 2 < Оҙ) :
    CauchySeq g := by
  refine' Metric.cauchySeq_iff'.2 fun Оө hОө => _;
  obtain вҹЁ N, hN вҹ© := hg_komlos ( Оө^2 / 8 ) ( by positivity );
  -- By the properties of the norm and the parallelogram law, we can show that the distance between $g_n$ and $g_m$ is bounded.
  have h_dist : вҲҖ n m, N вүӨ n вҶ’ N вүӨ m вҶ’ вҖ–g n - g mвҖ– ^ 2 < Оө ^ 2 / 2 := by
    intro n m hn hm
    have h_norm_sq : вҖ–(2вҒ»В№ : в„қ) вҖў (g n + g m)вҖ– ^ 2 = (1 / 4) * (вҖ–g nвҖ– ^ 2 + вҖ–g mвҖ– ^ 2 + 2 * inner в„қ (g n) (g m)) := by
      rw [ @norm_smul, norm_eq_sqrt_real_inner ] ; norm_num ; ring;
      rw [ @norm_add_sq в„қ ] ; ring;
      norm_num ; ring;
    rw [ @norm_sub_sq в„қ ];
    have := hN n m hn hm; norm_num at *; linarith!;
  exact вҹЁ N, fun n hn => by rw [ dist_eq_norm ] ; exact lt_of_le_of_lt ( Real.le_sqrt_of_sq_le ( le_of_lt ( h_dist _ _ hn le_rfl ) ) ) ( by rw [ Real.sqrt_lt' ] <;> nlinarith ) вҹ©

-- The original statement is missing the [CompleteSpace E] hypothesis.
-- Without completeness, the Cauchy sequence produced by komlos_convex (via the parallelogram law)
